  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a pistol shrimp that shoots bubbles at hordes of underwater enemies in this unique blend of genres! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will gain experience points to level up your crustacean and choose upgrades such as attack damage or movement speed. Crack open oysters to collect pearls to spend unlocking new shrimps and weapons after your run!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Top-down, 2D, Vector art and underwater photography.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Twin Stick multi-directional shooter, Roguelite.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3418640/extras/c5d7f84b7ab616b83afd27a02146f42e.avif?t=1747098058\" width=180 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(Several user reviews are personal friends.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as a pistol shrimp that shoots bubbles at hordes of underwater enemies in this unique blend of genres! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will gain experience points to level up your crustacean and choose upgrades such as attack damage or movement speed. Crack open oysters to collect pearls to spend unlocking new shrimps and weapons after your run!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Top-down, 2D, Vector art and underwater photography.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Twin Stick multi-directional shooter, Roguelite.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3418640/extras/c5d7f84b7ab616b83afd27a02146f42e.avif?t=1747098058\" width=180 height=85 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >(Several user reviews are personal friends.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
